Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.05,0:00:11.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I am a man of sin.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.86,0:00:14.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A single woman comes to my doorstep to court me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.56,0:00:17.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A friend through long years \Nof language study—
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.33,0:00:18.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}is it time to move beyond?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.41,0:00:22.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Have I ever been the recipient of an attack \Nby a person of such charms before?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.25,0:00:25.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}However, before my eyes is another woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.79,0:00:30.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She came to me out from under that \Nother man, and she speaks all but naught.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.06,0:00:34.43,Dialogue,,120,120,0,,{\i1}And indeed, there is yet another woman whose feelings are wedging into a corner of my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.91,0:00:41.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She is, even now, waiting and waiting \Nfor me to come to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.68,0:00:45.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dear God! Is it a sin for \Na man to be so popular?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.26,0:00:46.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What ever shall I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.16,0:00:48.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on out!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.40,0:00:51.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Decide already!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.85,0:00:55.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Outside the door is the sexy Hanuki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.57,0:00:57.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In the boarding house is the silent, exquisite, Kaori-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.32,0:01:00.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And waiting at the café is my \Nyet unseen pen-pal, Keiko-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.62,0:01:03.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Unless I plan on becoming \Na renaissance man of the sexual arts,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.86,0:01:05.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I must narrow it down to one of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.42,0:01:06.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.12,0:01:08.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In that case!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.63,0:01:10.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I choose Keiko-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.59,0:01:12.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.90,0:01:14.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I will not succumb to the flesh!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.56,0:01:19.30,Dialogue,,120,120,0,,{\i1}What I should do now is to strip away all veneer and reveal myself as I am at this moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.30,0:01:22.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Keiko-san, please wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.84,0:01:24.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then I was a brand-spanking-new freshman university student,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.57,0:01:28.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and countless doors to that rose-colored campus life lay open before me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.02,0:01:30.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}However, devoting my life to a single circle
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.15,0:01:33.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}poses a chance of wasting \Nmy entire college life in vain.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.48,0:01:34.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}One must spread out the risk!
Dialogue: 2,0:01:34.65,0:01:38.58,Dialogue,,0,0,30,,{\i1}I will join many circles and experience a diversified rose-colored campus life!
