Dialogue: 2,0:01:41.28,0:01:44.86,Dialogue,,0,0,65,,{\i1}As I have always been of the indoor variety, \NI will search for encounters through reading!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.46,0:01:49.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Books are the ocean! Now is the time to set sail on the sea of the printed word!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.57,0:01:53.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The waves of life, the wind, the sad rain, \Nthe storm of trials, the hopeless Sargasso...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.64,0:01:55.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1\t(2160)}The meetings and partings of a ria coast!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.26,0:02:04.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1\t(1670)}The morning sun of hope...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.70,0:02:07.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then, one day, I encounter a single small ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.90,0:02:10.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And on that ship, a raven-haired maiden.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.00,0:02:17.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.97,0:02:20.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Reading is, after all, a solitary journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.22,0:02:22.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But don't you think this is a little too quiet?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.27,0:02:25.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The seeds of love can't sprout here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.68,0:02:27.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm alone adrift on the Pacific!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.33,0:02:33.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks, come again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.92,0:02:35.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Appreciate the business.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.98,0:02:37.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you'd like, read this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.80,0:02:41.93,Book,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,250)\1a&HFF&\blur0.4}"The Night Is Brief, Go Forth Maidens," by Morimi Tomihiko
Dialogue: 1,0:02:37.80,0:02:41.93,Book,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,250)\bord0\blur0.4}"The Night Is Brief, Go Forth Maidens," by Morimi Tomihiko
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.25,0:02:40.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a silly little young-adult novel,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.41,0:02:43.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but feel free to use it as \Na bad example to follow.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.31,0:02:44.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Get out of my sight!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.77,0:02:50.27,Dialogue,,120,120,0,,{\i1}He said he'd bought it at a used book store \Nand didn't need it anymore, so I should read it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.27,0:02:52.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Its content was that of \Na silly little young-adult novel,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.66,0:02:55.99,Dialogue,,120,120,0,,{\i1}but on the final page was an address and name, \Nwritten in exquisite penmanship.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.99,0:02:57.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It seemed to be that of the previous owner.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.65,0:03:00.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I become strangely curious of this Higuchi Keiko-san person.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.43,0:03:04.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have long been envious of those \Nengaging in the exchange of letters.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.56,0:03:07.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The dreamer in me itched to trade carefully crafted communiques
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.45,0:03:09.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}if, by some unforeseen chance, an opportunity should arise.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.25,0:03:11.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When I expressed this wish \Nto Ozu in the past...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.25,0:03:15.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It must be exciting to send off lewd prose \Nto a woman you don't even know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.97,0:03:19.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're such a hopeless deviant. What am I to do with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.30,0:03:21.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You ribald writing wretch!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.37,0:03:23.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...is how he called me a giant pervert.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.07,0:03:25.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I saw it as an excellent chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.94,0:03:27.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is not this, indeed, the command of heaven?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.69,0:03:31.44,Dialogue,,120,120,0,,{\i1}Is not forming a pen-pal with an unseen woman \Na once-in-a-lifetime opportunity?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.73,0:03:30.23,Exchange Letters,,0,0,0,,{\org(639,469)\fad(0,500)\be1\t(1000,1500,\frz90)\move(638.664,323.197,737.537,398.141,1000,1482)}E\Nx\Nc\Nh\Na\Nn\Ng\Ne
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.73,0:03:30.23,Exchange Letters,,0,0,0,,{\org(639,469)\fad(0,500)\be1\t(1000,1500,\frz90)\move(662.714,323.197,716.159,400.818,1000,1482)}L\Ne\Nt\Nt\Ne\Nr\Ns
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.69,0:03:31.44,Exchange Letters,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\be0.7\fsp9\frz-90\t(0,500,\frz0\c&HAD3AE5&)\move(638.664,323.197,575.198,368.699,0,606)}Exchange
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.69,0:03:31.44,Exchange Letters,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\be0.7\fsp9\frz-90\t(0,500,\frz0\c&HAD3AE5&)\move(638.664,323.197,575.198,388.773,0,606)}Letters
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.09,0:03:36.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But sending off a letter unannounced is, \Nat the least, unrefined, or simply freakish.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.12,0:03:38.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And so I purchased stationery \Nthat was beautiful,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.82,0:03:41.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and to make up for that freakishness overflowing with sincerity,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.66,0:03:44.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wrote a letter containing harmless pleasantries.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.57,0:03:47.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}First, I apologized profusely \Nfor sending a letter uninvited,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.48,0:03:50.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}then added a note explaining \Nhow I was a hardworking student,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.83,0:03:54.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and, neither praising or criticizing, \Ngave my impressions of the novel I finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.57,0:03:57.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wrote nothing of requesting to receive a response.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.28,0:03:59.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As a lengthy missive would give off \Na somewhat freakish vibe,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.38,0:04:02.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wrote revision after revision, aiming for a mere half a page.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.38,0:04:13.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It requires considerable resolve to send a reply to a letter
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.17,0:04:16.99,Dialogue,,120,120,0,,{\i1}that was sent to you from an unknown person \Nin this world of corrupt morals.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.22,0:04:20.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even more if it's some maiden \Nraised among butterflies and rainbows.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.99,0:04:24.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was prepared not to feel hurt if a response did not come.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.50,0:04:34.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dear you, thank you for the letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.45,0:04:37.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Through this letter, \NI could tell from her modesty
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.65,0:04:41.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}that Keiko-san was herself \Na lovely raven-haired maiden.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.86,0:04:43.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Bingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.11,0:04:49.31,Dialogue,,120,120,0,,{\i1}And so, from such an unbelievably simple start, my two years exchanging letters had begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.43,0:04:53.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The hot and humid days continue on,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.74,0:04:56.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}like summer is coming \Njust a step ahead, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.35,0:04:58.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In my boarding house, \Nthere is quite poor ventilation,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.94,0:05:00.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}so it is considerably hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.25,0:05:06.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It became quite humid after \Nthe Hollyhock Festival ended, yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.29,0:05:07.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Before the rainy season comes,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.41,0:05:10.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have a sense we're stuck \Nwandering in the doldrums of summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.47,0:05:12.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I think being able to study \Nwhatever you'd like in college
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.96,0:05:15.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}is a really amazing thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.37,0:05:18.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What are you studying there?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.40,0:05:22.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My studies are nothing particularly special.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.10,0:05:24.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I am majoring in agriculture.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.52,0:05:26.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I am deeply interested in \Nthe world of science.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.83,0:05:31.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I feel it a shame that one is not able to \Nsurvey it all because it has grown vastly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.63,0:05:35.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Such progress is what enables \Nour modern way of life, however,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.12,0:05:36.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}so I must make due.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.77,0:05:40.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It sounds like your studies are quite wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.43,0:05:44.82,Dialogue,,120,120,0,,{\i1}As for me, a lecturer who has been in Japan for three years was returning to his home country,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.82,0:05:48.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and we threw a farewell party at an Irish pub on Oike Street.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.80,0:05:51.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I cannot imbibe,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.04,0:05:54.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but the fried whitefish was very delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.16,0:06:00.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have never been to an Irish pub before, \Nbut I do wish to go one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.42,0:06:02.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have much interest in the culture of England.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.85,0:06:07.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I hope to one day go there myself and \Ntest out the fruits of my language study.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.73,0:06:10.66,Dialogue,,120,120,0,,{\i1}Thanks to my father's work, I spent a short time \Nin New York during my childhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.66,0:06:14.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was raised greatly admiring Miles Davis and Magic Johnson (has it already been so long?),
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.75,0:06:17.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and I remember skating there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.74,0:06:21.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I use that experience to teach at an inter-college English-conversation circle.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.76,0:06:26.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I feel like my experience might be of \Nsome small help to the other students.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.59,0:06:29.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So you've lived overseas?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.86,0:06:31.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I think that's really amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.58,0:06:35.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But it's not good for your health if you strain yourself by studying too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.75,0:06:37.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Be careful not to overdo it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.60,0:06:39.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thank you for your concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.32,0:06:42.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As you say, I am also engaging in \Nwhat physical activity I may.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.34,0:06:45.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Actually, as a way to relieve stress, \NI enjoy playing the part of an action star.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.72,0:06:48.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I know it's childish and laughable,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.04,0:06:49.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but it's a Hero TV show!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.71,0:06:52.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It gives me a chance to train my body, \Nand at the same time,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.08,0:06:54.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can let children live their dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.36,0:06:56.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It is a job worth doing, indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.60,0:06:59.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wish to teach children that justice will prevail!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.17,0:07:17.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, save Mochiguman!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.34,0:07:19.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, what's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.30,0:07:22.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those bad guys are trying to kidnap the girl, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.92,0:07:25.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone, make them change their ways!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.92,0:07:29.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Change your ways! \NChange your ways! Change your ways!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.92,0:07:32.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Change your ways! Change your ways!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.84,0:07:36.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look, they ran away!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.84,0:07:35.53,Dialogue Alt,,0,0,0,,Change your ways! Change your ways!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.53,0:07:37.85,Dialogue Alt,,0,0,0,,Change your ways!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.11,0:07:37.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good job, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.45,0:07:40.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Mochiguman!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.11,0:07:47.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you, kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.86,0:07:49.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.02,0:07:50.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Weirdo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.12,0:07:51.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Think he's some freak?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.36,0:07:54.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It sounds like a wonderful activity.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.71,0:07:59.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I also love heroes that make children happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.06,0:08:02.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Although I, too, am embarrassed by my childish taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.82,0:08:05.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As the letters came from Keiko-san, \Nso too did my glimpses at her personality.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.76,0:08:08.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She was, indeed, my ideal woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.55,0:08:12.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wrote about myself, \Ntrying to be as appealing as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.11,0:08:13.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Although there were some slight embellishments,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.31,0:08:15.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}they were all for the sake of \Nclassy presentation, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.17,0:08:18.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You've been beaming lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.77,0:08:20.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Something happen of note?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.31,0:08:22.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of note or notes,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.10,0:08:23.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,it's none of your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.85,0:08:26.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's not like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.08,0:08:29.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You are exchanging letters with \Na mystery woman you've never met, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.11,0:08:30.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How do you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.32,0:08:31.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seems I hit the mark.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.68,0:08:36.22,Dialogue,,120,120,0,,Well, doing it by exchanging letters is \Nprobably perfect for a spineless wimp like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.22,0:08:38.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I am not doing these \Nrude things you think I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.70,0:08:43.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, now, I know you. \NPorn comprises half of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.15,0:08:45.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even now, you're anguishing over wanting to meet her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.58,0:08:47.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You wouldn't be able to understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.50,0:08:49.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a platonic relationship!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.90,0:08:54.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Said I, while at the same time being in \Na close relationship with two other girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.22,0:08:57.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You should just go with your feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.64,0:09:00.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hanuki-san's English was left \Na bit too much to her feelings;
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.10,0:09:03.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}a miraculous master of soul talk who expressed herself perfectly to the instructor.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.31,0:09:06.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, so you and Ozu-kun are in the same year?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.00,0:09:07.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a small world, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.40,0:09:09.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's a patient at our practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.44,0:09:12.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks to his meddling, \NI've gotten in a ton of trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.73,0:09:15.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tell me about it. That's his hobby.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.00,0:09:17.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And he has a habit of keeping secrets about himself, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.65,0:09:20.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't even know where he lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.18,0:09:21.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He won't tell me no matter how much I ask!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.72,0:09:24.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, I've been there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.32,0:09:25.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.04,0:09:26.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's in Joudoji.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.83,0:09:31.05,Dialogue,,120,120,0,,A bit farther in off of Shirakawa Road is an \Napartment building that looks like it's made of candy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.05,0:09:33.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like Ozu-kun gets \Na lot of money from his parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.92,0:09:35.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can he piss me off any more?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.56,0:09:38.90,Dialogue,,40,40,0,,{\i1}Hanuki-san, with whom I was having frank conversations, is an older, lovely dental hygienist.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.90,0:09:41.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We started going to a café together after class.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.24,0:09:48.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then, because of the Hero Show, \NI came to take care of a certain woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.73,0:09:50.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let me introduce you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.14,0:09:51.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is Kaori.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.48,0:09:54.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kaori is a very elegant woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.09,0:09:55.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I want you to be very courteous to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.06,0:09:58.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.32,0:09:59.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't go getting any weird thoughts now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.85,0:10:04.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}According to Mr. Jougasaki, who hired me, I was exceedingly cautious and a safe bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.08,0:10:05.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Her hair was carefully combed,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.98,0:10:07.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and her clothes were neat and elegant.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.64,0:10:09.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I couldn't think of her as a doll at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.16,0:10:12.68,Dialogue,,120,120,0,,{\i1}It's not like I couldn't understand how \NMr. Jougasaki could be so enthralled with this beauty.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.89,0:10:17.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ozu-kun doesn't drink, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.88,0:10:18.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What about you, Hanuki-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.86,0:10:21.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It causes problems for me, \Nso I only drink with people I'm close to.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.02,0:10:24.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you need a drinking buddy, I'd be happy to, anytime!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.22,0:10:26.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not so easy to handle...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.98,0:10:28.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Someone she's close to, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.52,0:10:30.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I haven't entered that category yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.86,0:10:35.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No, one day, Hanuki-san and I will drain a barrel of Yamazaki Distillery whiskey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.02,0:10:41.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Man, your place stinks!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.89,0:10:44.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Continuing from long ago, an enemy of the Masochistic Proxy-Proxy War
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.93,0:10:48.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}had infiltrated Mr. Jougasaki's \Nboarding house and with hidden cameras,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.26,0:10:51.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}filmed scenes of him caring for his \Ndear Kaori-san and screened an exposé.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.80,0:10:54.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure you got the balls for it,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.38,0:10:56.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but my place isn't safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.40,0:10:58.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold on to Kaori here \Nfor a little while, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.78,0:11:00.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kaori, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.88,0:11:04.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know this place is filthy, \Nbut please endure it for a little while.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.08,0:11:07.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Suddenly, we began living together.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.52,0:11:10.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The game of Love had taken \Nsuch a sudden turn,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.98,0:11:13.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but my letters with Keiko-san also continued unabated.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.26,0:11:16.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There are two crucial points about exchanging letters.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.09,0:11:18.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The first is that they must be handwritten.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.48,0:11:20.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And the second is that,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.12,0:11:22.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}for example, even if the cauldron of hell is unleashed and the world comes to an end,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.88,0:11:24.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}to ne'er meet your partner in correspondence.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.98,0:11:28.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Says I, but it is only human to \Nbecome curious about your partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.03,0:11:29.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What is she like?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.55,0:11:33.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What does she wear? What is her home like? \NHow does she walk? What does she look like?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.92,0:11:35.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I want to know more!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.07,0:11:41.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Only once did I head toward her address.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.62,0:11:42.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It was impulsive.
