Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.42,0:11:52.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.68,0:11:53.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.23,0:11:58.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wasn't that Akashi-san? \NI wonder if she recognized me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.97,0:12:01.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Akashi-san was in the class \None year below me,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.15,0:12:02.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}together with Ozu in the engineering department.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.81,0:12:04.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I had thought it a pressing question as to
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.82,0:12:07.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}why she ended up hanging out \Nwith a person like him
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.02,0:12:10.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and visiting a person on the second floor of Shimogamo Yuusuisou they call "Master."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.99,0:12:15.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Anyway, I had thought I would continue \Nmy platonic relationship with Keiko-san, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.90,0:12:16.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Greetings.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.88,0:12:19.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Spring sure is in full bloom.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.21,0:12:21.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's already been two years
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.80,0:12:23.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}since we've started this \Nback-and-forth of letters.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.87,0:12:27.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There is something I want to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.29,0:12:29.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Could we meet up, face to face, one time?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.85,0:12:31.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.85,0:12:35.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I surely caught her fancy \Nthrough my genius literary skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.26,0:12:36.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I am entirely a man of sin.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.14,0:12:40.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I cannot meet her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.09,0:12:45.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The me in the letters had walked far away from the me in reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.05,0:12:47.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I had originally written the \Nhigh expectations of myself
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.76,0:12:50.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I predicted would be true \Nby the time I met Keiko-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.56,0:12:52.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but at some point, it had become pure fabrication.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.25,0:12:55.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.87,0:13:01.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I cannot disillusion Keiko-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.18,0:13:02.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have lied far too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.74,0:13:04.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't show my face to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.21,0:13:06.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But she gathered the courage \Nand wrote "I want to see you!"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.98,0:13:08.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why am I, a man, being so indecisive?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.98,0:13:12.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's still not too late! \NI'll become the me who's in the letters!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.12,0:13:13.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's it, I'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.88,0:13:16.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then I'll become a man worthy of her!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.36,0:13:20.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}However, the hurdles were far too high.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.44,0:13:23.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why did I even write those things in the letters to begin with?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.24,0:13:28.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Keiko-san kept repeating the invitation, \Nand I kept dodging the issue.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.47,0:13:30.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, wanna go out for some drinks?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.17,0:13:33.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was finally asked out \Nfor a drink by Hanuki-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.41,0:13:36.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This certifies that she feels close to me now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.26,0:13:37.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.28,0:13:40.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have a report that I need to write today.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.52,0:13:41.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.85,0:13:45.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right. Good luck on your report!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.64,0:13:58.15,Letter 2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(151,0)\fax0.4\be1.2\frx4\fry0}I can wait no longer. I want to tell you. I'll be waiting \Nat Cafe Collection on August 13th at 8 p.m. \N_If perchance you do not come, let us no longer \N_persist in this exchange of letters.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.64,0:13:58.15,Letter 2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(222,28)\fax0.4\be1.2\frz279}'
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.15,0:13:59.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That meeting is tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.68,0:14:02.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But today is my last day with Kaori-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.62,0:14:05.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The other day, Mr. Jougasaki came to say he was taking Kaori-san back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.48,0:14:08.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We are being torn apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.04,0:14:10.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder if you'll forget about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.30,0:14:14.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was being forced into making a decision \Nabout all three women at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.06,0:14:17.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I think about the past two years. \NWhat a sweet, innocent two years I had led.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.21,0:14:20.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now that it's finally come to this, \Neverything is hurtling toward the climax!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.67,0:14:22.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Do I go for drinks with Hanuki-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.17,0:14:23.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Do I take Kaori-san and run away?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.67,0:14:26.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Do I meet Keiko-san and \Nreveal the whole truth to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.45,0:14:28.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Unless I plan to become \Na renaissance man of the sexual arts,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.57,0:14:30.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I must narrow it down to one of them!
Dialogue: 1,0:14:30.44,0:14:34.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So if it's like this, I'd rather have \Nsome guy who asks me out every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.43,0:14:35.43,Kubouzuka,,0,0,0,,{\pos(489.687,384.089)\be1.4\frz286.741}Kubouzuka
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.43,0:14:35.43,Kubouzuka,,0,0,0,,{\an7\pos(285.261,215.465)\fs30\c&H505659&\be1.4\fscx88\frz286.741}I'm in the hotel lounge right now. \NWant to come for a drink? (^_−)〜☆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.43,0:14:38.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I had a sinking feeling like she was falling \Ninto the clutches of that perverted dentist.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.94,0:14:41.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hanuki-san must've wanted moral support!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.66,0:14:44.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't let her be ruined by the \Ninvitations of the perverted dentist!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.09,0:14:45.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is a matter of life and death!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.25,0:14:47.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I cannot stand idly by and watch it unfold!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.31,0:14:48.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,First thing: consult the old woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.74,0:14:50.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That'll be 6,000 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.49,0:14:57.50,Scrolling Text 2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,375)\alpha&HFF&\frx70\fscy215\t(\fscy0)\p1}m 0 0 l 1 0 1 95 0 95{\fscy\p0} \N{\be0.7\alpha\t(2000,3000,\alpha&HFF&)}Went to lounge, drinking contest with {\c&H621BEA&}Jougasaki{\c&HEFF2EF&}, a tough battle but won, \N{\alpha\t(3000,4000,\alpha&HFF&)}then dragged around by {\c&H621BEA&}Hanuki{\c&HEFF2EF&}-san, ended up at her {\c&H621BEA&}apartment{\c&HEFF2EF&}, \N{\alpha\t(4000,5000,\alpha&HFF&)}but with a "{\c&H621BEA&}Keiko{\c&HEFF2EF&}-san!" I ran out of her {\c&H621BEA&}bathroom
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.50,0:15:02.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've made up my mind! \NI'll show her my true self!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.77,0:15:07.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Searching for someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.51,0:15:09.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's you! Didn't I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.13,0:15:12.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The opportunity is always \Ndangling in front of your eyes.
