Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.10,0:15:17.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Her apartment! You have to \Nsurprise her at her apartment!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.10,0:15:18.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Out of the question!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.15,0:15:20.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Visiting the home of your pen-pal is completely unacceptable!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.84,0:15:22.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's breaking the most fundamental rule!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.69,0:15:23.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I absolutely will not!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.32,0:15:28.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Go! Yahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.54,0:15:31.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Rules are made to be broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.76,0:15:34.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Keiko-san lives up there, in room 306.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.63,0:15:38.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I am going to show Keiko-san \Nthe real me if it's the last thing I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.54,0:15:44.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It was then that I saw Keiko-san with an extremely eerie face—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.90,0:15:46.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}an unhealthy looking face
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.08,0:15:48.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}that seemed like it belonged to \Na human from the dark side of the moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.64,0:15:51.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It had an ominous smile rising up that seemed like it was entreating other's misery.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.24,0:15:53.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'd say it was strangely slippery \Nlike some youkai's.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.00,0:15:54.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She almost looked like Ozu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.38,0:15:56.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She and Ozu were two peas in a pod. Or rather she was exactly like Ozu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.78,0:15:58.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No, that {\i0}is{\i1} Ozu!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.84,0:16:01.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Swallowing the conclusion \NI had come to within my mind
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.74,0:16:03.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}required a great amount of effort from my soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.85,0:16:07.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I needed a whole cup full of sugar to make this unimaginably bitter medicine go down!
