Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.17,0:16:14.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Could there be a more cruel conclusion?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.13,0:16:17.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Senpai! It's you, right, Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.20,0:16:19.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akashi-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.35,0:16:20.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I apologize for deceiving you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.42,0:16:23.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I am sorry,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.76,0:16:26.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but I participated in the exchange of letters.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.09,0:16:28.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wrote the letters at the request of Ozu-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.80,0:16:31.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As I felt pained from these actions,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.86,0:16:33.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I could not bring myself to say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.43,0:16:34.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.38,0:16:35.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So it was you, Akashi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.86,0:16:36.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.74,0:16:37.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.94,0:16:39.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But Ozu is the only one at fault, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.97,0:16:43.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, Ozu-senpai got bored of it after a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.35,0:16:45.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was just a random prank to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.74,0:16:48.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I could not bring myself to simply fade out,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.12,0:16:51.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so I took over writing \Nthe letters as Keiko-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.63,0:16:53.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that's what it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.11,0:16:55.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was quite difficult \Ncapturing Keiko-san's character.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.68,0:16:58.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After all, Ozu-senpai knew \Nyour tastes extremely well
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.42,0:17:00.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and had used them to \Ncreate the character.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.86,0:17:04.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's true. Keiko-san was my ideal woman, \Nfar too good to be true.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.29,0:17:06.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But to think that it was \NOzu who created her?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.38,0:17:08.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since you didn't come \Nto where I said to meet,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.30,0:17:12.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought you might stop by here, \Nso I staked it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.99,0:17:17.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was saved by you once.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.25,0:17:19.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you remember the Mochiguman Show?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.64,0:17:21.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.22,0:17:24.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was still in high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.40,0:17:27.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought you were really cool \Nback then, Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.79,0:17:32.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That... was me while I was in the suit...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.83,0:17:34.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The real me is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.40,0:17:37.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was a lot of fun exchanging letters.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.00,0:17:39.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's true you like to show off a little,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.33,0:17:41.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but I was lying as well,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.10,0:17:42.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so we're even.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.06,0:17:50.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,These come in sets of five, \Nbut I lost one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.09,0:17:52.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I really love Mochiguman.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.55,0:17:53.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's kind of embarrassing, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.10,0:17:59.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Opportunity is always \Ndangling in front of your eyes.
