Dialogue: 1,0:18:11.11,0:18:13.61,Letter,,0,0,0,,{\pos(412.881,166.617)\fax-0.1\fay0.19\be0.8\frz47.18\frx16\fry356}I collected Kaori-san. \N\N{\fs32}The castella is a reward {\fs31}\N\Nfrom Jougasaki-san. \N\N\N\NOzu
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.05,0:18:16.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why'd you go straight home?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.06,0:18:17.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That was a pretty nice moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.61,0:18:19.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why didn't you at least \Nask her out on a date?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.04,0:18:24.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't misunderstand.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.19,0:18:27.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akashi-san just likes Mochiguman. That's all. It's not me she likes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.69,0:18:28.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.78,0:18:31.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm tearin' outta here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.10,0:18:48.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn you, Ozu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.06,0:18:50.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When I think about it, enough Keiko-san, enough Hanuki-san or Kaori-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.92,0:18:54.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Could it be that I was just \Ndancing in the palm of Ozu's hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.24,0:18:55.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That goddamn monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.54,0:18:58.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Eating the unhappiness of others \Nas a topping on his three helpings of rice!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.09,0:18:59.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now that I think about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.13,0:19:02.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}he must've had quite a delicious feast \Nfrom me these past two years!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.63,0:19:04.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He deserves to die \Na thousand times over!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.12,0:19:05.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll roast him into coffee \Nand grind him to bits!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.26,0:19:08.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Silently, I ate the entire castella myself
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.58,0:19:10.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and, through my actions, \Nsank deeper into a hellish solitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.72,0:19:14.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As I devoured the castella, \NI took on the form of a devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.88,0:19:19.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's right. Don't misunderstand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.54,0:19:22.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was enamored with Keiko-san whom was created by Ozu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.52,0:19:25.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It was most definitely not Akashi-san. \NDon't change the subject.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.23,0:19:28.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Longing for others, transiently wishing for a partner... I will not accept it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.89,0:19:32.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}After all, it is my fate to be dragged down forever together with Ozu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.89,0:19:32.90,The Mariana Trench,,0,0,0,,{\an2\pos(149.645,48.848)\p1\c&H852D29&\blur1.5}m 158.625 432 l 197.375 454.625 349.375 459.375 434.625 453.375 460 428.625 433.375 410.625 180.625 412.625
Dialogue: 1,0:19:30.89,0:19:32.90,The Mariana Trench,,0,0,0,,{\pos(170,431.599)\be0.8}The Mariana Trench
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.06,0:19:35.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When I thought that, \NI found myself strangely relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.02,0:19:36.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm not suited to stand on \Nlove's victory podium.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.72,0:19:38.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is how it should be...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.53,0:19:39.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like hell it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.68,0:19:42.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I want to stand on the victory podium, no matter what methods I have to use!

